<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 20:06:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>卡塔尔和沙特阿拉伯呼吁就以色列军队拉法入侵可能召开联合国安理会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-10/ty-article/qatar-and-saudi-arabia-call-to-convene-un-security-council-over-possible-rafah-invasion/0000018d-93f7-d9cc-a5cd-f7ffade40000</link><description>哈马斯控制的卫生部表示，周六，44 名巴勒斯坦人在加沙南部城市拉法被杀，几小时前，内塔尼亚胡要求军方在地面入侵之前计划撤离那里的数十万人。</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 19:23:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-10/ty-article/qatar-and-saudi-arabia-call-to-convene-un-security-council-over-possible-rafah-invasion/0000018d-93f7-d9cc-a5cd-f7ffade40000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 127 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-127/0000018d-9426-d9cc-a5cd-f5be501e0000</link><description>信用评级机构穆迪表示正在降低以色列的信用评级 ■ 来自加沙的报道称，以色列国防军在拉法杀死了哈马斯警察情报局长 ■ 以色列军队和辛贝特表示，他们发现哈马斯隧道系统穿过近东救济工程处加沙中部总部下方■ 战争开始 127 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 18:09:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-127/0000018d-9426-d9cc-a5cd-f5be501e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称，在近东救济工程处加沙总部下方发现了哈马斯隧道，官员办公室内藏有武器</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article/.premium/idf-says-it-uncovered-hamas-tunnel-under-unrwa-gaza-hq-weapons-in-officials-offices/0000018d-93fe-d57f-a1ef-bbfea7aa0000</link><description>以色列宣布这一消息之前，曾多次指控近东救济工程处与加沙地带的巴勒斯坦激进组织有联系，这导致该组织的许多顶级捐助者暂停为其提供资金。 近东救济工程处负责人拉扎里尼回应：该机构“不知道”什么在其总部下，工作人员于 10 月在以色列撤离命令后逃离</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 18:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article/.premium/idf-says-it-uncovered-hamas-tunnel-under-unrwa-gaza-hq-weapons-in-officials-offices/0000018d-93fe-d57f-a1ef-bbfea7aa0000</guid></item><item><title>被哈马斯扣押的以色列人质家属在政治版图双方的协助下加紧战斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article/.premium/families-of-hamas-hostages-step-up-their-fight-aided-by-both-sides-of-the-political-map/0000018d-935f-d443-a19f-ffdff9c10000</link><description>随着左翼活动分子占领特拉维夫的主要道路，右翼抗议者试图阻止对加沙的人道主义援助，争取新人质协议的斗争变得比以往任何时候都更加激烈</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 16:16:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article/.premium/families-of-hamas-hostages-step-up-their-fight-aided-by-both-sides-of-the-political-map/0000018d-935f-d443-a19f-ffdff9c10000</guid></item><item><title>如果以色列军队入侵拉法，那里避难的超过150万巴勒斯坦人将何去何从？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/if-israel-invades-rafah-what-will-be-of-over-1-5m-palestinians-who-take-shelter-there/0000018d-9360-d443-a19f-fff113ba0000</link><description>以色列对拉法的入侵将导致近百万巴勒斯坦平民惊慌失措地大规模逃往大约本古里安机场大小的指定安全区。目前尚不清楚以色列国防军计划如何将其与国际法院的命令相协调，即以色列必须采取一切措施避免种族灭绝行为</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 15:40:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/if-israel-invades-rafah-what-will-be-of-over-1-5m-palestinians-who-take-shelter-there/0000018d-9360-d443-a19f-fff113ba0000</guid></item><item><title>穆迪致以色列：是政府，笨蛋！</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article/.premium/moodys-to-israel-its-the-government-stupid/0000018d-92ee-d9cc-a5cd-f7fe76460000</link><description>为了保住权力，内塔尼亚胡不顾一切地支持以色列的宗教法西斯分子，并坚持敬畏上帝的经济政策。结果是以色列有史以来首次信用评级被下调</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 13:13:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article/.premium/moodys-to-israel-its-the-government-stupid/0000018d-92ee-d9cc-a5cd-f7fe76460000</guid></item><item><title>以色列边境警察杀害了一名 4 岁巴勒斯坦女孩，10 天后才归还她的尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-02-10/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-cops-killed-a-4-year-old-palestinian-girl-then-took-10-days-to-return-her-body/0000018d-90dd-d443-a19f-fcdd3cf20000</link><description>边境警察向一辆试图闯过检查站的车辆不分青红皂白地开枪，还向一辆载着一名母亲和她的孩子的出租车发射了 32 发子弹。其中一名小女孩被枪杀</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 03:26:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-02-10/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-cops-killed-a-4-year-old-palestinian-girl-then-took-10-days-to-return-her-body/0000018d-90dd-d443-a19f-fcdd3cf20000</guid></item><item><title>“内塔尼亚胡，我们不会给你片刻的和平”：抗议者封锁特拉维夫高速公路，纵火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article-live/netanyahu-israels-economy-is-strong-credit-downgrade-is-only-due-to-war/0000018d-90d4-d57f-a1ef-b8dce9aa0000</link><description>加沙报道：以色列国防军在拉法杀死了哈马斯警察情报局长和另外两人 ■ 以色列国防军表示，以色列北部响起的数十个空中渗透警报是误报 ■ 叙利亚人权观察组织称，大马士革附近的以色列空袭造成三人死亡 ■ 穆迪下调以色列信用评级首次</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 03:01:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article-live/netanyahu-israels-economy-is-strong-credit-downgrade-is-only-due-to-war/0000018d-90d4-d57f-a1ef-b8dce9aa0000</guid></item><item><title>“抗议结束战争，母亲结束战争。”更多的以色列人应该呼吁结束这种疯狂行为”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/protests-end-wars-moms-end-wars-more-israelis-should-call-for-an-end-to-this-madness/0000018d-9052-d443-a19f-fcd3789c0000</link><description>以色列单口喜剧演员诺姆·舒斯特-埃利亚西在阿拉伯世界也颇有名气，他呼吁人们不要再忽视对方的悲伤</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 02:31:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/protests-end-wars-moms-end-wars-more-israelis-should-call-for-an-end-to-this-madness/0000018d-9052-d443-a19f-fcd3789c0000</guid></item><item><title>“我的人头要出价”：数百名普通以色列人因血仇而躲藏起来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/theres-a-price-on-my-head-these-ordinary-israelis-are-in-hiding-due-to-blood-feuds/0000018d-8fb8-d9cc-a5cd-ffba41150000</link><description>他们是守法的以色列阿拉伯公民——医生、律师、教师——由于涉及家人的致命争斗，他们无法离开罗德城的家</description><pubDate>Sat, 10 Feb 2024 00:01:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-10/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/theres-a-price-on-my-head-these-ordinary-israelis-are-in-hiding-due-to-blood-feuds/0000018d-8fb8-d9cc-a5cd-ffba41150000</guid></item><item><title>穆迪历史上首次下调以色列信用评级，展望下调至“负面”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/moodys-downgrades-israels-credit-rating-for-first-time-in-countrys-history/0000018d-8eb1-d57f-a1ef-bebde2450000</link><description>穆迪决定不仅降低以色列的信用评级，而且还下调其信用前景，这让耶路撒冷的官员感到意外。虽然现在确定此举的财务影响还为时过早，但这对以色列的国际形象造成了严重打击</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 21:46:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/moodys-downgrades-israels-credit-rating-for-first-time-in-countrys-history/0000018d-8eb1-d57f-a1ef-bebde2450000</guid></item><item><title>2016年逃往加沙的以色列贝都因人被捕，被指控加入哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-bedouin-who-fled-to-gaza-in-2016-arrested-accused-of-joining-hamas/0000018d-8f14-d57f-a1ef-bf1c2a2c0000</link><description>Juma Ibrahim Abu-Ganima 在 12 月试图返回以色列后被拘留。他被指控向哈马斯提供有关以色列南部以色列国防军基地的信息</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 18:59:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-bedouin-who-fled-to-gaza-in-2016-arrested-accused-of-joining-hamas/0000018d-8f14-d57f-a1ef-bf1c2a2c0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 126 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-126/0000018d-8ea2-d