-02-09/ty-article/.premium/how-u-s-policy-on-gaza-war-has-polarized-opinion-in-israel-america-and-the-arab-world/0000018d-8e52-d443-a19f-fed3458b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军调查发现人质很可能在空军轰炸中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/idf-investigation-reveals-high-probability-that-hostage-killed-during-air-force-bombing/0000018d-8e4d-d9cc-a5cd-ffffe7840000</link><description>以色列军队认为，约西·沙拉比在以色列国防军对他和另外两名人质被关押的地方附近的一栋建筑进行袭击时被杀</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 15:02:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/idf-investigation-reveals-high-probability-that-hostage-killed-during-air-force-bombing/0000018d-8e4d-d9cc-a5cd-ffffe7840000</guid></item><item><title>战时以色列的愤怒正在上升，以色列人必须去战斗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/anger-is-rising-in-wartime-israel-about-which-israelis-must-go-and-fight/0000018d-89a7-d9cc-a5cd-fdbf2eb20000</link><description>自加沙战争开始以来，许多预备役军人已经穿了四个月的军装，以色列的极端正统派和世俗社区正在就谁必须在以色列国防军服役的问题发生冲突。总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡已经在努力集结军队</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 14:33:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/.premium/anger-is-rising-in-wartime-israel-about-which-israelis-must-go-and-fight/0000018d-89a7-d9cc-a5cd-fdbf2eb20000</guid></item><item><title>联合国表示，加沙近 10% 的五岁以下儿童现在严重营养不良</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/almost-10-percent-of-gazas-under-fives-now-acutely-malnourished-un-says/0000018d-8e04-d1e0-a3ff-9ffff73a0000</link><description>由于食品卡车经常遭到饥饿人群的围攻，救援人员报告说，儿童有明显的饥饿迹象，特别是在加沙北部和中部地区</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 13:57:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/almost-10-percent-of-gazas-under-fives-now-acutely-malnourished-un-says/0000018d-8e04-d1e0-a3ff-9ffff73a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列空袭加沙拉法，美国警告不要在该市进行地面行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/israeli-airstrikes-hit-gazas-rafah-as-u-s-warns-against-ground-operation-in-city/0000018d-8d83-d9cc-a5cd-fdbb03d70000</link><description>连夜空袭造成 22 人死亡，袭击了拉法的两栋住宅楼，并损坏了一座由幼儿园改建的流离失所巴勒斯坦人避难所</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 11:47:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-09/ty-article/israeli-airstrikes-hit-gazas-rafah-as-u-s-warns-against-ground-operation-in-city/0000018d-8d83-d9cc-a5cd-fdbb03d70000</guid></item></channel></rss>